---
title: 'Blogroll'
pageTitleClasses: 'text-center'
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
layout: 'layouts/wider-content-page.njk'
---

{% if collections.blogroll | length %}
  <p class="text-center">
    Cool people I follow online and how to find them.
    Their work and writing makes me hopeful about the future of the web.
  </p>
  <div class="container bg-dark p-l text-light">
    <div class="grid">
          {% for person in collections.blogroll | sort(collections.blogroll, false, false, 'title' ) %}
            <article class="card" data-card-variant="blogroll">
              <div class="card__content flow">
                <div class="card__heading">
                  <em>{{ person.latest_post.published | simpleDate if person.latest_post.published}}</em>
                </div>
                <div class="card__meta">
                  <p>
                    {{ person.title }}
                  </p>
                  </a>
                </div>  
                  {% if person.latest_post.url %}
                    <div>
                      <a href="{{ person.latest_post.url }}" target="_blank" style="text-wrap: wrap;">
                        {{ person.latest_post.title if person.latest_post.title else person.latest_post.url }}
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
              </div>
            </article>
          {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>    
{% else %}
  <p>The blogroll appears to be empty. Check back later to see the cool people I follow online.</p>
  <a href="/">‚Üê Back to homepage</a>
{% endif %}